<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 12:12:28 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>解救以色列人质并在纽约大型集会上发表讲话，纪念 10 月 7 日六周年纪念日</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/rescued-hostage-to-address-major-n-y-rally-to-mark-six-month-anniversary-of-october-7/0000018e-a38c-dadc-a7af-fbafd4370000</link><description>来自各个政治和宗教领域的犹太机构和组织将聚集在联合国总部外参加大规模集会。由于犹太人在这个问题上达成了一致共识，组织者能够确保议程相互冲突的团体参与</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 11:22:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/rescued-hostage-to-address-major-n-y-rally-to-mark-six-month-anniversary-of-october-7/0000018e-a38c-dadc-a7af-fbafd4370000</guid></item><item><title>为什么最近的反内塔尼亚胡抗议活动尚未成为群众运动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/whats-preventing-the-latest-anti-netanyahu-protests-from-becoming-massive/0000018e-9fc1-d4c8-adce-fff5d9000000</link><description>尽管大多数以色列人对内塔尼亚胡没有信心，但四年来针对他和他的政府的第三波抗议活动尚未看到数十万人走上街头。这不仅是因为总理仍在设法引导有关加沙战争的公开辩论</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 10:48:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/whats-preventing-the-latest-anti-netanyahu-protests-from-becoming-massive/0000018e-9fc1-d4c8-adce-fff5d9000000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方考虑对参与人质、反政府抗议活动的议员进行刑事调查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/police-mulls-criminal-investigation-of-lawmaker-for-participating-in-anti-govt-protest/0000018e-a367-df93-a9af-b77f70340000</link><description>警方称，MK Naama Lazimi 被拍到在周六举行的示威活动中纵火。 “我建议警方调查那些故意阻止人质交易并让他们（哈马斯）慢慢杀害我们 134 名俘虏的人。 Ben-Gvir - 我不怕你，”她说</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 10:46:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/police-mulls-criminal-investigation-of-lawmaker-for-participating-in-anti-govt-protest/0000018e-a367-df93-a9af-b77f70340000</guid></item><item><title>揭开“加沙”这个名字的由来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/unraveling-the-origins-of-the-name-gaza/0000018e-a33c-ded0-a18f-e3fc704f0000</link><description>加沙是一座历史悠久的城市，自始至终它都有过不同的名字。穿越时间的语言之旅可能会带来意想不到的词源</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 09:46:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/unraveling-the-origins-of-the-name-gaza/0000018e-a33c-ded0-a18f-e3fc704f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高法院裁定不得释放受制裁寡头罗曼·阿布拉莫维奇的资金</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/top-court-rules-against-releasing-sanctioned-oligarch-roman-abramovichs-funds/0000018e-a2e0-d9c2-afbe-aaf6ef430000</link><description>该裁决推翻了法院此前向该银行发出的命令，要求该银行将罗曼·阿布拉莫维奇的 800 万谢克尔捐款转给 ZAKA 搜救组织。该裁决指出，尽管受到制裁，但批准这笔捐赠将“使银行面临各种风险”</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 08:48:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/top-court-rules-against-releasing-sanctioned-oligarch-roman-abramovichs-funds/0000018e-a2e0-d9c2-afbe-aaf6ef430000</guid></item><item><title>以色列应用程序提供半价餐食，只要你吃剩菜</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/tech-news/2024-04-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/app-offers-meals-at-half-price-as-long-as-youll-eat-leftovers/0000018e-9f68-ded0-a18f-dff84a1a0000</link><description>SpareEat 表示，其目标是防止食物浪费并应对高昂的生活成本。用户必须适应并且不能太挑剔</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 07:25:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/tech-news/2024-04-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/app-offers-meals-at-half-price-as-long-as-youll-eat-leftovers/0000018e-9f68-ded0-a18f-dff84a1a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列中部地区发生冲撞和刺伤袭击，四名以色列警察受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/four-israeli-police-officers-wounded-in-ramming-and-stabbing-attack-in-central-israel/0000018e-a228-d6b5-a39f-bf796f600000</link><description>这名 26 岁的以色列裔阿拉伯人袭击者在 444 号公路上继续袭击，试图袭击附近检查站的警卫后被部队开枪打死。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 04:44:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/four-israeli-police-officers-wounded-in-ramming-and-stabbing-attack-in-central-israel/0000018e-a228-d6b5-a39f-bf796f600000</guid></item><item><title>甚至在以色列杀害加沙援助人员之前，世界就已经对以色列失去了耐心</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/even-before-israel-killed-aid-workers-in-gaza-the-world-was-running-out-of-patience/0000018e-a06e-d4f2-a9cf-b87e0a960000</link><description>以色列担心，在希法医院遭受破坏之后发生的世界中央厨房事件将增加国际社会的压力，要求在不确保人质获释和哈马斯政权不结束的情况下结束这场运动。将伊朗拖入一场它不希望的战争</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 03:01:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/even-before-israel-killed-aid-workers-in-gaza-the-world-was-running-out-of-patience/0000018e-a06e-d4f2-a9cf-b87e0a960000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯可能在两天内回应加沙停火、与以色列达成人质协议的提议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/hamas-response-to-gaza-truce-hostage-deal-proposal-with-israel-likely-within-two-days/0000018e-a052-d9c2-afbe-a8d64e800000</link><description>参与谈判的一位消息人士表示，这种回应的性质将决定协议能否迅速敲定，但警告称，到目前为止，双方立场之间的分歧“巨大”</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 03:00:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/hamas-response-to-gaza-truce-hostage-deal-proposal-with-israel-likely-within-two-days/0000018e-a052-d9c2-afbe-a8d64e800000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在加沙发现的哈马斯档案详细记录了被指控为同性恋的高级成员的处决情况</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-04-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/hamas-files-found-by-israel-in-gaza-detail-execution-of-senior-member-accused-of-being-gay/0000018e-9e6d-d64e-afce-fffd62370000</link><description>马哈茂德·伊什蒂维 (Mahmoud Ishtiwi) 于 2016 年被处决，此后哈马斯一直试图对此事保密。以色列军方在加沙隧道中发现了记录他的痛苦经历的文件，并显示哈马斯继续折磨据信是同性恋的成员</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 03:00:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-04-03/ty-article-magazine/.premium/hamas-files-found-by-israel-in-gaza-detail-execution-of-senior-member-accused-of-being-gay/0000018e-9e6d-d64e-afce-fffd62370000</guid></item><item><title>以色列辛贝特主席警告抗议活动中存在暴力，人质家庭扰乱议会辩论</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article-live/four-police-officers-injured-two-seriously-in-terror-attack-in-central-israel/0000018e-a1bd-d38b-afff-e1bf80690000</link><description>西班牙外长：我们将承认巴勒斯坦是一个主权国家，因此将在联合国占有一席之地 ■ 哈马斯消息人士称，以色列的新提议不会导致停火谈判取得突破 ■ 四名以色列警察在冲撞、刺伤袭击中受伤■ 拜登对加沙援助人员的死亡感到“愤怒和心碎” ■ 以色列国防军负责人为“无意杀害”援助人员道歉</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 02:29:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article-live/four-police-officers-injured-two-seriously-in-terror-attack-in-central-israel/0000018e-a1bd-d38b-afff-e1bf80690000</guid></item><item><title>据报道，美国大亨削减资金后，司法政变背后的以色列智囊团限制了业务</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/as-donations-dry-up-think-tank-behind-israels-judicial-coup-scales-back-operations/0000018e-a141-d176-adcf-a14d08d50000</link><description>据报道，保守派智库科赫莱特政策论坛是内塔尼亚胡政府削弱司法机构的关键参与者，该论坛正在解雇数十名研究人员，并削减对其他支持类似目标的右翼组织的支持</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 00:17:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/as-donations-dry-up-think-tank-behind-israels-judicial-coup-scales-back-operations/0000018e-a141-d176-adcf-a14d08d50000</guid></item><item><title>被杀的埃塞俄比亚裔以色列青少年的家人谴责枪杀他的警察无罪释放</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/family-of-slain-ethiopian-israeli-teen-decry-acquittal-of-police-officer-who-shot-him/0000018e-a078-ded0-a18f-e2f88fef0000</link><description>所罗门·特卡 (Solomon Teka) 在 2019 年公园的一起事件中被杀。他的妹妹在谈到判决时表示，“警方现在有权杀害儿童”</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 23:08:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/family-of-slain-ethiopian-israeli-teen-decry-acquittal-of-police-officer-who-shot-him/0000018e-a078-ded0-a18f-e2f88fef0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军方消息人士：加沙援助人员被杀是因为“以色列国防军军官在当地为所欲为”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-02/ty-article/.premium/idf-sources-gaza-aid-workers-killed-because-officers-on-the-ground-do-what-they-want/0000018e-a06e-d9c2-afbe-a8fe319b0000</link><description>以色列国防军和国防部声称援助人员被杀是由于协调不力造成的。以色列军方消息人士后来驳斥了他们的说法，称该事件“与协调无关”，而是“每个指挥官都为自己制定规则”造成的。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 20:49:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-02/ty-article/.premium/idf-sources-gaza-aid-workers-killed-because-officers-on-the-ground-do-what-they-want/0000018e-a06e-d9c2-afbe-a8fe319b0000</guid></item><item><title>如果以色列将所有加沙受害者视为公关灾难就好了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-04-02/ty-article/.highlight/if-only-israel-thought-of-all-its-gaza-victims-as-a-pr-disaster/0000018e-9fe4-d4c8-adce-fff46a8a0000</link><description>以色列对七名世界中央厨房援助人员在以色列袭击中丧生的反应与其对之前整个加沙冲突期间发生的人道主义悲剧的反应形成鲜明对比</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 19:44:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-04-02/ty-article/.highlight/if-only-israel-thought-of-all-its-gaza-victims-as-a-pr-disaster/0000018e-9fe4-d4c8-adce-fff46a8a0000</guid></item><item><title>数百名以色列人在内塔尼亚胡位于耶路撒冷的家外抗议，警察与人质家庭发生冲突；五人被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-02/ty-article/.premium/police-hostage-families-clash-as-hundreds-rally-outside-pm-home-in-jerusalem-5-arrested/0000018e-9feb-d4f2-a9cf-bfff4a830000</link><description>数百名抗议者中断了数千名以色列人参加的示威活动，呼吁提前举行选举并立即达成人质协议，这是为期四天的大规模反政府集会的一部分</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 18:52:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-02/ty-article/.premium/police-hostage-families-clash-as-hundreds-rally-outside-pm-home-in-jerusalem-5-arrested/0000018e-9feb-d4f2-a9cf-bfff4a830000</guid></item><item><title>惠誉确认以色列信用评级，但给予其负面展望</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/business/economy-finance/2024-04-02/ty-article/.premium/fitch-affirms-israels-credit-rating-but-assigns-it-a-negative-outlook/0000018e-9fb8-d4f2-a9cf-bfbe09860000</link><description>国际评级机构批评内塔尼亚胡政府，称联盟的不稳定阻碍了财政整顿。 “尽管赤字激增，2024 年预算修正案仍包括一些与联盟相关的支出”</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 17:49:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/business/economy-finance/2024-04-02/ty-article/.premium/fitch-affirms-israels-credit-rating-but-assigns-it-a-negative-outlook/0000018e-9fb8-d4f2-a9cf-bfbe09860000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗对真主党和叙利亚的关键人物：据称在大马士革被以色列暗杀的最高将军是谁？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-02/ty-article/.premium/irans-point-man-to-hezbollah-who-is-the-top-general-allegedly-assassinated-by-israel/0000018e-9f9c-d9c2-afbe-bfde685a0000</link><description>扎赫迪20岁时加入革命卫队，担任空军指挥官、地面部队指挥官和作战部门负责人。在他最后的职位上，他是圣城军叙利亚和黎巴嫩指挥官，被认为与纳斯鲁拉关系特别密切</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 17:45:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-02/ty-article/.premium/irans-point-man-to-hezbollah-who-is-the-top-general-allegedly-assassinated-by-israel/0000018e-9f9c-d9c2-afbe-bfde685a0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登“将向以色列明确表示”必须保护加沙援助人员；美国期待“全面”公开调查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-04-02/ty-article/.premium/u-s-demands-swift-probe-u-k-summons-israeli-envoy-world-reacts-to-wck-attack/0000018e-9f72-ded0-a18f-dff2c6500000</link><description>该非政府组织表示，周一，世界中央厨房的七名工作人员在以色列对加沙中部的空袭中丧生，其中包括来自澳大利亚、英国和波兰的公民。英国已召见以色列大使，阿联酋宣布将停止海上援助路线的努力</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 16:35:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-04-02/ty-article/.premium/u-s-demands-swift-probe-u-k-summons-israeli-envoy-world-reacts-to-wck-attack/0000018e-9f72-ded0-a18f-dff2c6500000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 179 天：将向哈马斯提出新的停火提案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-02/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-179-new-cease-fire-proposal-to-be-presented-to-hamas/0000018e-9f6f-d4f2-a9cf-bf7f33f30000</link><description>以色列空袭导致加沙七名国际援助人员死亡 ■ 以色列国防军调查发现，保护车队的部队误认为武装恐怖分子与他们同行 ■ 以色列发动的空袭导致伊朗在叙利亚的高级将军丧生，伊朗最高领导人表示，以色列“将对这次袭击感到遗憾” ■ 摩萨德称将向哈马斯提交新的停火/释放人质提案 ■ 战争结束 179 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 16:26:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-02/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-179-new-cease-fire-proposal-to-be-presented-to-hamas/0000018e-9f6f-d4f2-a9cf-bf7f33f30000</guid></item></channel></rss>